old text-primary mb-4\">Creative content</h3>\n<ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-600 text-sm\">\n<li>\u2022 Campaign narrative that feels authentic to your mission</li>\n<li>\u2022 Landing page strategy and messaging</li>\n<li>\u2022 Email sequence designed as journey, not collection of separate messages</li>\n<li>\u2022 Social strategy reflecting different platform strengths and audiences</li>\n<li>\u2022 Visual direction maintaining brand consistency while creating campaign identity</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<!-- Column 3 -->\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100\">\n<div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-pale-yellow rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary\">\n<svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n</path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Complete journey design</h3>\n<ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-600 text-sm\">\n<li>\u2022 Pre-campaign phase building awareness and interest</li>\n<li>\u2022 Campaign launch coordinated across channels</li>\n<li>\u2022 Mid-campaign momentum maintenance</li>\n<li>\u2022 Post-campaign follow-up deepening relationships</li>\n<li>\u2022 Thank you and impact communication that extends beyond campaign</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<!-- Column 4 -->\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100\">\n<div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-pale-yellow rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary\">\n<svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3